OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fcloudy across all parts through the
OL,7,Fevening with outbreaks of mainly light
OL,8,Frain spreading east overnight. Chance
OL,9,Fof some heavier bursts of rain in the
OL,10,Ffar west after dawn. Breezy and
OL,11,Fstaying mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FCloudy at first, some
OL,14,Fintermittent rain in places. More
OL,15,Fpersistent rain, with embedded heavier
OL,16,Fpulses, spreads east during the day,
OL,17,Ffollowed by brighter conditions and
OL,18,Fscattered, possibly thundery showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
